stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> CollectEvidence
  CollectEvidence --> CheckQuality
  CheckQuality --> ModelConsensus
  ModelConsensus --> NonModelEvidence
  NonModelEvidence --> DisagreementReview
  DisagreementReview --> FinalLabel

  FinalLabel --> likely_real: Real evidence dominates
  FinalLabel --> likely_ai_generated: AI evidence crosses threshold
  FinalLabel --> likely_manipulated_or_deepfake: Manipulation evidence dominates
  FinalLabel --> inconclusive: Evidence weak, noisy, or conflicted
